Class LinkedListWithIterator<T>

java.lang.Object
LinkedListWithIterator<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, ListInterface<T>, ListWithIteratorInterface<T>
public class LinkedListWithIterator<T> extends Object implements ListWithIteratorInterface<T>
A class that implements the ADT list by using a chain of linked nodes. The list has an iterator. The class is similar to LList.
Version:
5.0
Author:
Frank M. Carrano, Timothy M. Henry
